SUMMARY:[Canceled] Davis Makerspace Drop In Hours
DTSTART;TZID=PST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260305T093000
DTEND;TZID=PST;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260305T113000
UID:8222c60d53f283357e30edd9b122b528@events.yolocountylibrary.org
DESCRIPTION:Today's Hours are canceled due to staff shortage. 3D prints th
 at are finished may be picked up at the front desk. We apologize for the i
 nconvenience. \n\n \n\nDavis Makerspace is a community workspace for mak
 ers and builders\, designers and inventors. A small assortment of tools wi
 ll be available for use and staff or volunteers will be on hand to provide
  some assistance. Supervised children are welcome. Participants must provi
 de a signed liability waiver (available on site).\n\n \n\nClothing Repair
  coaching is available on Mondays\, Tuesdays and Thursdays during Drop In 
 Hours.
LOCATION:YoloLab Makerspace\, Mary L Stephens Davis Branch Library
URL:https://events.yolocountylibrary.org/event/15972781
X-SOURCE:Yolo Library
END:VEVENT
