SUMMARY:SOF Annual Iftar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260306T000000Z
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260306T030000Z
UID:dfbeb54a42bce2f34cd6b76029ba50941212026_1:14:57_AM@campusgroups.com
DESCRIPTION:It will be an open (tracked with RSVP Form) campus iftar at UC
  Davis\, offering a free\, communal dinner for students and faculty of all
  backgrounds. The event will highlight the mission of advocating for Afgha
 n girls’ education while creating a warm and inclusive space where guest
 s can learn\, connect\, and share in the experience of breaking fast. Thro
 ugh food\, conversation\, and community\, the evening will celebrate unity
 \, understanding\, and the shared hope for freedom and opportunity for all
 .
URL:https://aggielife.ucdavis.edu/rsvp?id=908185
X-SOURCE:UC Davis CampusGroups
END:VEVENT
