SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260306T065708Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260308T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260308T150000
SUMMARY:Art in Action: Celebration Stations Part 2
DESCRIPTION:Pence Family Art Workshops\nShow your love for the arts by dec
 orating the perfect containers for your art supplies and other craft items
 ! Learn the art of decoupage by experimenting with tissue paper\, scrapboo
 k paper\, fabric\, dried flowers\, paint pens\, and more.\n\nArt in Action
 : Celebration Stations Part 2\nSunday\, March 8\, 1-3 PM\n$5 Members\, $10
  Non-Members (per person\, all materials included)\n\n**How it works:**\nA
 rt in Action engages kids in art projects that are fun\, creative\, and co
 llaborative with their family members. This is a drop-in program for ages 
 5-12. No registration in advance is required\, but space and supplies are 
 limited to the first 25 participants and are available on a first come\, f
 irst served basis.\n\nWhen you arrive\, pay with cash or card at the front
  desk. A parent or adult caregiver is required to stay\, but only has to p
 ay for the project for themselves if they are also doing art. Stay as long
  or as short as you like over the two hour period.\n\nBecome a Member star
 ting at $70/year and save! If you join the Pence Gallery when you attend t
 his workshop\, you can enjoy Member pricing for Art in Action\, plus recei
 ve a $5 gift certificate to our gift shop as a thank you! Membership suppo
 rts art for all ages and makes creative moments like this possible—jump 
 in and be part of it.\n\nWe have a different Art in Action family workshop
  every month! Learn more at [https://pencegallery.org/art-in-action/](http
 s://pencegallery.org/art-in-action/).\n\nThis unique monthly program is ge
 nerously sponsored and made possible by Mary Stephens DeWall and Les DeWal
 l.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/art-in-action/events/313194446/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260203T213426Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260203T213426Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
