BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Davis Downtown": "https://davisdowntown.com/event/2nd-friday-artabout/2026-03-13/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:davis_downtown
SUMMARY:2nd Friday ArtAbout – Monthly Downtown Davis Art Walk & Receptio
 ns (Free!)
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260313T170000Z
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260313T210000Z
UID:10000169-1773421200-1773435600@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:Join Davis’s beloved 2nd Friday ArtAbout – a free monthly 
 self-guided artwalk coordinated by the Pence Gallery! Every second Friday\
 , stroll downtown Davis to discover fresh exhibits\, opening receptions\, 
 live music\, hands-on activities\, and direct chats with local and regiona
 l artists at 10+ galleries\, co-ops\, and businesses. \nSupport our vibran
 t arts scene\, uncover unique talent and styles\, and soak up the lively e
 nergy – ideal for friends\, families\, dates\, or solo adventures. Many 
 venues offer complimentary refreshments like wine and snacks. \nFree – n
 o tickets required! \n\nRuns approximately 5:00–9:00 PM (venue reception
 s vary—check the monthly guide for specifics).\nGrab the printed guide (
 with map & details) the week of at the Pence Gallery or participating spot
 s\, or download it at pencegallery.org/events/artabout/.\n\nInterested in 
 hosting as a venue\, artist\, or business? Visit https://pencegallery.org/
 events/artabout/ to fill out the corresponding forms. Please submit event
 s 3 weeks in advance via the form on the site to be included in the guide 
 and promotions. \nStay in the loop: facebook.com/davisartabout \nCome cele
 brate local creativity downtown – see you on the next second Friday! 
 🎨✨
LOCATION:CA
URL:https://davisdowntown.com/event/2nd-friday-artabout/2026-03-13/
X-SOURCE:Davis Downtown
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Davis Chamber": "https://web.davischamber.com/events/2nd%20Friday%20ArtAbout%20at%20the%20Pence%20Gallery-5702/details"}
X-SOURCE-ID:davis_chamber
SUMMARY:2nd Friday ArtAbout at the Pence Gallery
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260313T180000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260313T210000
UID:2b216eaa1e907b227c71b96a882f5ef4@davischamber.com
DESCRIPTION:Community Event\n\nJoin us at the Pence Gallery for our 2nd Fr
 iday ArtAbout reception on March 13\, 6-9 PM. Enjoy browsing multiple art 
 exhibits\, complimentary wine by Matchbook Wines\, and an art-themed scave
 nger hunt. Also\, view special floral arrangements within the exhibits by 
 the Davis Flower Arrangers. Free admission!\n\nManuel Fernando Rios: When 
 They Reminisce Over You | Feb. 7 - Mar. 29\n\nThe artist’s work explores
  his Chicano heritage\, as well as his family’s history and experiences.
  Blurring the line between naturalism and abstraction\, he embraces the us
 e of complex design patterns and photography to make a powerful statement.
  \n\nAssorted Flavors: Pence Member Exhibit | Mar. 13 - Apr. 16\n\nOur 2n
 d annual non-juried exhibit celebrates the creativity and talent of our or
 ganization’s supporters\, showcasing work in different media by 40 Pence
  Members.\n\nBarbara Prodaniuk: Myths in Mud | Mar. 13 - Apr. 26\n\nThe ce
 ramic artist’s work is inspired by the forest\, meadows\, and waterways 
 surrounding the Truckee area. She explores the stories carried by the crea
 tures and artifacts found in these environments through layered surfaces\,
  organic textures\, and sculpted imagery.\n\nLoraine Watson-Fox: Small Won
 ders | Mar. 6 - Mar. 29\n\nThe artist employs mixed-media including collag
 e\, text\, thread and textural elements to enhance her use of more traditi
 onal paint media. Her work is on display along the stairway.\n\nDavis Flow
 er Arrangers: Art in Bloom | Mar. 13 - Mar. 15\n\nIn a special collaborati
 on\, the Davis Flower Arrangers have put together creative floral arrangem
 ents to be paired with specific artworks on view at the Pence.\n\nScavenge
 r Hunt: Join us for a fun\, art-themed scavenger hunt at the Pence during 
 the 2nd Friday ArtAbout. Complete all of the clues by exploring our exhibi
 ts for the chance to win a special prize.\n\n—\n\nVisit the Pence and ot
 her venues in Downtown Davis for the 2nd Friday ArtAbout artwalk. We will 
 have printed ArtAbout guides available that week. Follow the ArtAbout’s 
 Facebook page for more information: https://www.facebook.com/davisartabout
 .
LOCATION:212 D Street\, Davis\, CA 95616
URL:https://web.davischamber.com/events/2nd%20Friday%20ArtAbout%20at%20the
 %20Pence%20Gallery-5702/details
X-SOURCE:Davis Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
