SUMMARY:UC Davis Big Time
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260404T000000Z
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260404T060000Z
UID:62b042c472ca597f95ee4e49d79c8b021142026_1:30:15_PM@campusgroups.com
DESCRIPTION:UC Davis Powwow Committee\, American Indian Recruitment & Rete
 ntion (AIRR)\, and Native Dads Network are honored to invite you to the 1s
 t Annual UC Davis Big Time on Friday\, April 3rd\, 2026\, from 5 PM to 11 
 PM!\n\nCome experience an evening filled with Traditional California shake
  head dancers\, local Native vendors\, local organizations resource booths
 \, and a gathering that uplifts culture\, identity\, and community.\n\nThi
 s Big Time is more than an event\, it's a celebration of resilience and tr
 adition. Bring your family\, your friends\, and your good energy. We look 
 forward to seeing you there!
LOCATION:University Credit Union Center\, 1 Shields Ave\, Davis\, Californ
 ia 95616\, United States
URL:https://aggielife.ucdavis.edu/rsvp?id=908036
X-SOURCE:UC Davis CampusGroups
END:VEVENT
