SUMMARY:Emerging Topics: Pop-Up Talk
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260424T200000Z
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260424T210000Z
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51843766520718
DESCRIPTION:DataLab's pop-up talks are by DataLab faculty\, staff\, and af
 filiates and focus on emerging topics\, tips\, and trends in data science.
  Join us for the Winter 2026 series on alternating Fridays from 1-2 PM at 
 DataLab. After the talk stick around for refreshments during our weekly so
 cial "Data Science Cafe" from 2-3 PM.\n\n \n\nThis event is offered in per
 son. All members of the University of California system are welcome to att
 end. Advance registration requested but not required!\n\n \n\nCan’t atte
 nd this event? Materials from prior UC Davis DataLab workshops are availab
 le on DataLab's website. Check out our workshop schedule for other upcomin
 g trainings. Questions? Email datalab-training@ucdavis.edu. \n\n \n\nQuest
 ions? Contact datalab-training@ucdavis.edu.
LOCATION:Shields Library\, 360
URL:https://events.library.ucdavis.edu/event/pop-up-talk-w2026-0426
X-SOURCE:UC Davis Library
END:VEVENT
