X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup: Yolo Board Game Gathering": "https://www.meetup.com/yolo-county-board-game-gathering/events/mxnqstyjchbjb/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_board_games
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Yolo Board Game Gathering
UID:event_mxnqstyjchbjb@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260306T065707Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260506T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260506T210000
SUMMARY:Blood on the Clocktower at Blue Note
DESCRIPTION:Yolo County Board Game Gathering\nThe first Wednesday of every
  month\, we play _Blood on the Clocktower_\, a social deduction game in th
 e vein of Werewolf/Mafia/The Resistance\, with a few twists!\n\nWe'll have
  a circle of chairs reserved inside Blue Note\, near the back\, with a Yol
 o County Board Game Gathering sign on the table. Just say hello\, and we'l
 l show you some games\, pull some players together\, and get to having fun
 !\n\nWe also usually have a few tables of players playing other board game
 s\, if social deduction isn't your bag!\n\nGet a feel for Blood on the Clo
 cktower here: https://youtu.be/4sfa8_kNxsQ
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/yolo-county-board-game-gathering/even
 ts/mxnqstyjchbjb/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20250814T213807Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20250814T213807Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup: Yolo Board Game Gathering": "https://www.meetup.com/yolo-county-board-game-gathering/events/vwnqstyjchbrb/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_board_games
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Yolo Board Game Gathering
UID:event_vwnqstyjchbrb@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260306T065707Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260513T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260513T210000
SUMMARY:Weekly Game Night at Blue Note
DESCRIPTION:Yolo County Board Game Gathering\nUpdate 8/14/25:\n**We're sti
 ll active**\, but we primarily use Discord to chat and plan events. (See g
 roup description for invite link.)\n\nWe still meet every Wednesday for bo
 ard games at Blue Note Brewing Company. We'll have a handful of tables res
 erved near the back\; just look for the pile of board games.\n\nPeople usu
 ally start arriving around 5pm\, and games start whenever people are ready
 . Blue Note closes at 9pm\, and although we have a 5-10 minute grace perio
 d there\, you should be in the process of final scoring by 9\, or else pac
 k it up and play again another day.\n\nGame night is open to all ages! Blu
 e Note is a brewery\, not a bar\, so there's no restriction against minors
 . In addition to their crafted-in-house beer selection\, water and sodas a
 re available.\n\nYou're not required to buy anything in order to join us\,
  but we do encourage you to support local businesses. Blue Note's chef tea
 m makes a mean pizza\, and there are other nearby downtown restaurants and
  businesses.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/yolo-county-board-game-gathering/even
 ts/vwnqstyjchbrb/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20250814T213602Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20250814T213602Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
